com.google.ortools.constraintsolver

Class CastConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.ortools.constraintsolver.BaseObject
      • com.google.ortools.constraintsolver.PropagationBaseObject
        • com.google.ortools.constraintsolver.Constraint
          • com.google.ortools.constraintsolver.CastConstraint

  • public class CastConstraint
extends Constraint
    Cast constraints are special channeling constraints designed
    to keep a variable in sync with an expression. They are
    created internally when Var() is called on a subclass of IntExpr.
